\sum_{t=1}^{\infty}\beta^t\sum_{i=0}^{t-1}\alpha^i
\frac{\beta}{[(1-\alpha)(1-\alpha\beta)]}
\sum_{i=0}^{t-1}\alpha^i
\frac{1-\alpha^{t-1}}{1-\alpha}
\sum^{\infty}_{t=1}\frac{\beta^t(1-\alpha^{t-1})}{1-\alpha}
\sum_{t=1}^{\infty}\beta^t\sum_{i=0}^{t-1}\alpha^i = \sum_{t=1}^{\infty} \beta^t\frac{1-\alpha^t}{1-\alpha}= \frac{1}{1-\alpha}\left(\sum_{t=1}^{\infty} \beta^t - \sum_{t=1}^{\infty} (\alpha\beta)^t  \right) =\frac{1}{1-\alpha}\left(\sum_{t=0}^{\infty} \beta^t - \sum_{t=0}^{\infty} (\alpha\beta)^t  \right) 
